room_title: Escape room "Clown" by Big Escape Rooms in Washington, D.C.
room_description: Magento's circus was famous all around the globe with their best act involving talented Boris the Clown. After months of pretending to be happy over an over again, Boris couldn't take it anymore and went insane, killing all of the circus crew. Now he travels alone, luring audiences into his trap and playing games with the innocent victims before murdering them. Can you beat him at his own game and escape?
